---
subject: Infrastructure agent
releaseDate: '2023-06-01'
version: 1.42.2
---

A new version of the agent has been released. Follow standard procedures to [update the Infrastructure agent](/docs/infrastructure/install-configure-manage-infrastructure/update-or-uninstall/update-infrastructure-agent).

We recommends that you upgrade the agent regularly and at a minimum every 3 months. As of this release, the oldest supported version is [Infrastructure agent 1.27.0](https://docs.newrelic.com/docs/release-notes/infrastructure-release-notes/infrastructure-agent-release-notes/new-relic-infrastructure-agent-1270/).

## Added
Support Fluent Bit Use_ANSI flag in #1661
## Changed
Bump nri-flex version to 1.8.5 in #1668
Bump nri-prometheus version to 2.18.1 in #1665
Bump nri-docker version to 1.8.4 in #1660
## Fixed
msi checks performed before creating agent data directory in #1635
